<speech>
A thousand praises my heroes! You have destroyed the Ogre Lord and shattered the might of the Ogre
Horde. But beware for we cannot rejoice yet! You are still deep within the Ogre Fortress and the
alarm has now been raised. You must escape and if you can reach the surface you will be able to lead
the Emperor's forces against the remnants of the Ogre Horde.
</speech>
